@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram
title US15 â€“ Sequence Diagram (List Employees by Role)
autoactivate on
autonumber
actor "DGS Administrator" as ADM
participant ":AdminUI" as UI
participant ":StaffController" as Ctrl
participant ":StaffService" as Svc
participant ":StaffRepository" as Repo
activate ADM

note right of ADM : Initiates listing of employees by selected role
note right of UI : UI captures role filter and triggers request
note right of Svc : Applies business rules (validate role, etc.)
note right of Repo : Data access (findByRole)

ADM -> UI : Select role & request list >
UI -> Ctrl : listEmployeesByRole(role) >
Ctrl -> Svc : getEmployeesByRole(role) >
Svc -> Repo : findByRole(role) >
Repo --> Svc : List<StaffMember>
Svc --> Ctrl : List<StaffMember>
Ctrl --> UI : List<StaffMember>
UI --> ADM : Show staff list >

opt No staff members found
  Repo --> Svc : Empty list
  Svc --> Ctrl : Empty list
  Ctrl --> UI : Empty list
  UI --> ADM : Show "No employees for role" >
end

alt Invalid role
  Svc --> Ctrl : Error (InvalidRole) >
  Ctrl --> UI : Error (InvalidRole) >
  UI --> ADM : Show error message >
end

@enduml